title: Help get your employees cash without selling their shares
body:
Your employees need safe options for their equity and you don't want them to give up their shares. With Quid they:
✅ Receive cash for stock’s value 
✅ Pay no fees out-of-pocket 
✅ Keep their shares

We've helped shareholders from the following companies:
📈 Carta
💳 Credit Karma
🚙 Uber
🏠 Airbnb

Find out how to get funds for your pre-IPO shares today!
